---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
import AuthorBox from '../../components/AuthorBox.astro'
---
<Layout title="Full Agency AI Search Visibility Service | Rank4AI" description="AI search visibility across your website and the full digital ecosystem. Standard, Strategic and Partner engagements. Scope determined by audit.">

<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'What We Do', href: '/what-we-do/' },
      { label: 'Full Agency' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">Full Agency – Includes Site Work</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Full Agency Service</h1>

    <div class="bg-off-white border-l-3 border-l-teal rounded-lg p-6 mb-8 mt-6">
      <p class="text-[15px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">We work on your website and build your ecosystem. Standard from £1,500/mo. Scope set by audit.</p>
    </div>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">We work on your website directly. Technical changes, content restructure, authority architecture. Plus the full ecosystem build outside your site.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">Only need work outside your website? See <a href="/what-we-do/ecosystem-services/" class="link">Ecosystem Services</a>.</p>

    <h2 class="mb-4">How We Work</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">We work across three pillars. Depending on your audit, we focus on one, two, or all three.</p>

    <div class="space-y-4 mb-16">
      <div class="card-teal-border">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2">Technical Signal Engineering</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Making sure AI systems can find, crawl and correctly read your website. AI crawlers, structured data, Bing submission and the structural foundations that determine whether your content can be extracted and attributed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-teal-border">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2">Authority Architecture</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Structuring your website and content so AI systems can interpret what your business is, what it specialises in and how confidently they can summarise and cite it.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-teal-border">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-2">Ecosystem Signal Reinforcement</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Building the external signals across Google's platforms and the wider web that confirm your business independently across every platform that feeds the AI systems your customers use.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="mb-8 text-center">Engagement Levels</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-1">Entry</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-xl text-teal mb-3">From £800<span class="text-xs text-text-muted font-body"> / mo</span></p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mb-3">Ecosystem only. No site work.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">The right foundation for most businesses. Signals established, ecosystem active, AI platforms covered.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-1">Standard</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-xl text-teal mb-3">£1,500–2,500<span class="text-xs text-text-muted font-body"> / mo</span></p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mb-3">Audit-driven scope.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Technical implementation, content restructure, or subdomain content layer combined with the right ecosystem level.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card border-teal">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-1">Strategic</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-xl text-teal mb-3">£3,000–5,000<span class="text-xs text-text-muted font-body"> / mo</span></p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mb-3">Growth partnership.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Full technical implementation. 80-120 active touchpoints. Monthly AI appearance testing across all six platforms.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="!text-lg text-teal mb-1">Partner</h3>
        <p class="font-display text-xl text-teal mb-3">£5,000+<span class="text-xs text-text-muted font-body"> / mo</span></p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mb-3">Complete and continuous.</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Full rebuild, content to interpretation engineering standard, full ecosystem. 120-200+ touchpoints. Weekly AI testing.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-narrow">
    <h2 class="mb-4">What Builds Over Time</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">AI visibility is infrastructure, not a campaign. It compounds. The position built in month two is the foundation for month six. Unlike paid advertising, it does not stop when the budget stops.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-2"><span class="highlight">Months 1-2:</span> AI crawlers have access. Priority pages restructured. Google Ecosystem live and active.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-2"><span class="highlight">Months 2-4:</span> Content across key clusters to standard. Extended ecosystem building. All six platforms showing coverage.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-2"><span class="highlight">Months 4-8:</span> Full site and content to interpretation engineering standard. Full ecosystem active.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed"><span class="highlight">8 months plus:</span> Self-reinforcing. Very difficult for competitors to displace quickly.</p>
  </div>


    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/what-we-do/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Services</span></a>
        <a href="/what-we-do/ai-visibility-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">AI Visibility Audit</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">The Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-24 px-10 mt-16">
    <h2 class="mb-4">Get Started</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted mb-10 max-w-[500px] mx-auto">Every engagement begins with the AI Search Visibility Audit.</p>
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
    <p class="mt-4"><a href="/book-a-call/" class="link text-sm">Or book a call &rarr;</a></p>
  </div>
  <div class="container-narrow mt-8">
    <AuthorBox />
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
